Cookie: token={{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{sellBookId}}",
  "amount": 300,
  "bookTitle": "A Heritage of Biology",
  "customerName": "Aaishma Manandhar",
  "customerPhone": "9800000000",
  "customerEmail": "aaishmamanandhar023@gmail.com"
}

###

### 7.2 Initiate Payment – Missing bookId (Negative) → expect 400
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/initiate
Cookie: token={{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 490,
  "bookTitle": "No Book ID Test"
}

###

### 7.3 Initiate Payment – No Auth (Security Test) → expect 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/initiate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{sellBookId}}",
  "amount": 490
}

###

### 7.4 Cash on Delivery – Valid (Positive) → expect 200
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment/cod
Cookie: token={{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{sellBookId}}",
  "bookTitle": "A Heritage of Biology",
  "amount": 300,
  "sellerName": "Aaisha Manandhar",
  "buyerName": "Aaishma Manandhar",
  "delivery": {
    "name": "Aaishma Manandhar",
    "address": "Kathmandu, Baneshwor",
    "city": "Kathmandu",
    "pin": "44600",
    "phone": "9800000000"
  }
}

###

